Music video by Mbosso performing, “Pawa” (Power), is a heartfelt, poetic love song by Mbosso that captures the overwhelming power of deep affection. Using rich metaphors and smooth vocals, he likens love to an intoxicating force that leaves him weak and emotionally charged — “naishiwa pawa” (I’m losing power). The lyrics blend vulnerability with admiration, painting his lover as a source of strength and inspiration. With a melodic blend of Bongo Flava and soulful instrumentation, “Pawa” showcases Mbosso’s lyrical depth and emotive style.
